snippet.textDisplay:
Liverpool couldn't deal with the Jorge Jesus tactics for large spells.
Flamengo made our press redundant utilising your back four and wingers.
Our fullbacks were not as active as usual and I think we have to look at
Keita and Ox for this.
Hendo was the 6 and we didn't nearly have the output we usually do with Hendo on that right side of the midfield.

It was a superb game to watch.
I think fitness towards the end gave us the victory, we managed the press better than Flamengo and they got frustrated then failed to come back.
Great game. loved being in the tournament, it's very interesting and winning it means a lot.
